text.tspan: In this task, you will see letters.
Each letter is shown for a few
seconds. You need to decide if you saw
the same letter 2 trials ago, that is, this
If you saw the same letter 2 trials ago,
you press the "m" key. If you did it
correctly, you see green colors around
the letter. If you press the button when should not
press it, you will see "red" around the letter.
press the space bar to next info screen
To help you learn this task, at first there
is a very easy version. You will be
reminded of the letters you saw the
trials before. They come left from the
letter in the middle of the screen. They
are only there to help. Later on, they
will not be shown anymore, and you
need to do it all based on your memory.
press the space bar to next info screen
Now that you have learned the n-back
task, you need to do it purely based on
your memory. Thus, click the yellow letter
if it is the same as 2 letters ago.
Concentrate, because this is not easy!
press the button Q on your keyboard to start
